{"tid":1605951,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"成日都敗走，比黑警笑足一世","createTime":"2019-09-30T12:20:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-30T12:24:30.000Z","uid":260895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"78a47d3ae51a474231bced50c60ce8f835cdbcff","tid":1605951,"uid":260895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T12:20:38.000Z","msg":"次次一聽到有狗，個個走夾唔抖，笑死班黑狗。喂，大佬，我哋咁撚多人，下下都幾十萬計，唔係怕幾十隻狗呀嘛？我琴日無gear食咗兩次彈都無退縮過，點解要瘋狂走，下次嗌一二一二可唔可以係推進，唔係走佬？我哋已經被黑警笑到面都黃晒，唔好咁柒好無？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6f32cfbf950d65fe7284ed56548a5368a3ddb1d","tid":1605951,"uid":238275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T12:24:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}